data.description: Completely UPDATED home in Bradenton's desirable Mill Creek neighborhood offers privacy and tranquility! Located in an A-rated school district, this 3-bedroom home on an over-sized lot has an open concept kitchen with a large island that seats six and a walk-in pantry! The kitchen was recently updated with new cabinetry, granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances. Hardwood flooring runs throughout most of the home - the upstairs was just replaced with brand new wood flooring! All of the bathrooms were remodeled with new tile flooring, cabinetry and counter tops. The saltwater pool and spa overlook the wooded, landscaped yard which creates a private oasis! The pool and hot water heater are powered by solar to keep your electric bills low. The two-car garage has a large space that's perfect for a workshop or storage. This home has been impeccably maintained - brand new hot water heater, dishwasher and disposal; one of the dual a/c systems was recently replaced; lanai was re-screened (complete list of updates available). Enjoy all the amenities of Lakewood Ranch with NO CDD fees! Conveniently located near UTC, downtown Sarasota, beautiful beaches, shopping, dining and more.
